    "description": "<strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于游戏</h2></strong><br>这是玩家扮演的熊先生周游世界，以音乐为武器，挑战各国高手的传奇故事。<br>稻荷神社的守护武士，幽暗地牢的骷髅王，加勒比海上的海盗船长....<br>我们甚至还为每一主题关卡都相应使用了不同曲风：和风！三味线！Lo-Fi！HipHop！Trap！甚至还有雷鬼！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264950/extras/6247aa128bdbc19a25dcdaa624d01031.poster.avif?t=1720690396\" width=474 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264950/extras/6247aa128bdbc19a25dcdaa624d01031.webm?t=1720690396\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264950/extras/6247aa128bdbc19a25dcdaa624d01031.mp4?t=1720690396\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特色玩法</h2></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>打铁：踩着音乐节奏，与对手拼刀。</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264950/extras/75e7149d69048c39410b7b09a5807ec7.poster.avif?t=1720690396\" width=460 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264950/extras/75e7149d69048c39410b7b09a5807ec7.webm?t=1720690396\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264950/extras/75e7149d69048c39410b7b09a5807ec7.mp4?t=1720690396\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>武器：不同敌人攻击方式不一，玩家需要看穿敌人的各式攻击，随机应变。</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264950/extras/f19f9f85d4719840527af9e6c36d3207.poster.avif?t=1720690396\" width=460 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264950/extras/f19f9f85d4719840527af9e6c36d3207.webm?t=1720690396\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264950/extras/f19f9f85d4719840527af9e6c36d3207.mp4?t=1720690396\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>连打：在音乐的高潮处，玩家可以爽快的连续输出。</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264950/extras/bdb23fc63738a09e2b7e59a1e2284cc5.poster.avif?t=1720690396\" width=460 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264950/extras/bdb23fc63738a09e2b7e59a1e2284cc5.webm?t=1720690396\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264950/extras/bdb23fc63738a09e2b7e59a1e2284cc5.mp4?t=1720690396\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264950/extras/0afabee8a650ae078451c404b194abd4.poster.avif?t=1720690396\" width=460 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264950/extras/0afabee8a650ae078451c404b194abd4.webm?t=1720690396\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264950/extras/0afabee8a650ae078451c404b194abd4.mp4?t=1720690396\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
